<Grid
  xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
  xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">
<Grid.RowDefinitions>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="10"/>
        <RowDefinition Height="Auto"/>
    </Grid.RowDefinitions>
    <Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="10"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="*"/>
        <ColumnDefinition Width="Auto"/>
    </Grid.ColumnDefinitions>
	<!--TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Text="1985-8-18" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}"/-->
	<TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Left" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}">
		7 OCTOBER 1973
	</TextBlock>
    <!--TextBlock Grid.Row="1" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" HorizontalAlignment="Right" Text="05:00Z (06:00L)" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}"/-->

    <TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="발신:"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="3" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="이스라엘 해군함대 사령관"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="수신:"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="4" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="INS 미즈나크의 사령관 미첼 바르카이"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.Column="0" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="내용:"/>
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="7" Grid.Column="2" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" Text="새로운 명령 - 라타키아 공습"/>
	    <!--
	<Image Grid.Row="1" Width="250" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" Grid.RowSpan="6" Stretch="Uniform" HorizontalAlignment="Center" VerticalAlignment="Center" Source="{Binding Assets[ts_banner]}"/>
	-->
    <TextBlock Grid.Row="9" Grid.ColumnSpan="4" FontSize="{StaticResource Font.Size.Header}" TextWrapping="Wrap">
		기밀
		<LineBreak/>
		<LineBreak/>
		1. Israel is under attack on all fronts. Effective immediately, a state of war exists and you are authorized to sink any enemy ship encountered.
		<LineBreak/>
		<LineBreak/>
		2. Form Northern Task Force from 3rd Shayetet missile boats at Haifa, then proceed north at best speed to Latakia.
		<LineBreak/>
		<LineBreak/>
		3. 정보국은 최대 4대의 코마르급 미사일 고속정과 1대의 오사급 미사일 고속정이 스틱스(P-15 테르밋) 미사일을 장착한 것으로 보고 있습니다.
		<LineBreak/>
		<LineBreak/>
		4. Note: electronic surveillance has revealed a Soviet spy trawler nearby. This unit must not be engaged under any circumstances.
		<LineBreak/>
		<LineBreak/>
		5. 라타키아 항구에서 모든 시리아 군함을 끌어내어 침몰시키시오. 행운을 빕니다.
		<LineBreak/>
		<LineBreak/>
		기밀
	  </TextBlock>
</Grid>